data.description: Mandarin Gem! Located in a Cul-de-sac! Step into this inviting Mandarin home featuring new LVP flooring throughout! The spacious living room boasts a cozy fireplace, creating a warm ambiance. The updated kitchen, equipped with new appliances and countertops, adds a modern touch. A stylishly renovated guest bathroom enhances the home's appeal. Enjoy versatile rooms, including a dining area that easily transforms into an office. Outside, the backyard offers a serene pond view, enclosed by a privacy fence for your personal haven experience. Recent upgrades also includes a new roof in 2022 and an HVAC system in 2020 to ensure enhanced comfort and value for this charming residence. This one is a must see!!!
